        <!-- VISION -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Vision for Anthem Students</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Anthem families know that exceptional quality is worth the commute. With <strong>Gavilan Peak School</strong> officially phasing out its Mandarin Immersion program, families are looking for a sustainable alternative to keep the gift of language alive. Beibei Amigos is now the premier choice for parents willing to make the short drive south on I-17 to ensure their children don't miss the critical window for trilingual fluency. We fill the void left by the public school changes, preparing students for academic excellence at <strong>Anthem School</strong> or <strong>Great Hearts Anthem</strong> with a lifelong linguistic advantage they can no longer get locally.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <img src="https://www.beibeiamigos.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Beibei-Pouring-scaled.jpg" width="800" height="600" loading="lazy" alt="Preschool students near Anthem 85086" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover h-80">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- PROGRAMS -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-blue-50" id="programs">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-10">Beibei Amigos Trilingual Programs</h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
                     <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition h-full flex flex-col">
                        <div class="text-blue-500 mb-4 text-4xl"><i class="fas fa-cubes"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Traditional Program</h3>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">Designed for early learners, our Traditional Program uses play-based methods to naturally immerse children in <strong>Spanish and Mandarin</strong>. Through structured circle time, music, art, and storytelling, students build essential social skills and vocabulary.</p>
                        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">This pathway emphasizes group interaction and emotional development, making it perfect for families in 85086 seeking a joyful introduction to school and early socialization.</p>
                     </div>
                     <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition h-full flex flex-col">
                        <div class="text-green-500 mb-4 text-4xl"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Montessori Program</h3>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">Strictly following Maria Montessori's philosophy, this program fosters independence, concentration, and self-directed learning. Children work with specialized materials to master math, literacy, geography, and practical life skills—all taught trilingually.</p>
                        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">This academic track is the gold standard for <strong>Kindergarten readiness</strong>, specifically designed to prepare students for the rigor of <strong>Anthem School</strong> or <strong>Great Hearts Academy</strong>.</p>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- KEY INFO SECTION -->
        <section class="py-12 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                    <!-- Ages -->
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="text-2xl">👥</span> Ages
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            We welcome <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">toddlers (1 year walking to 2 years old)</span> and <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">preschoolers (3 to 5 years old)</span>. All programs feature full language immersion in Spanish, Mandarin, and English.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Hours -->
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="text-2xl">🕐</span> Hours
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-2">
                            Our school is open <span class="font-bold text-green-600">7:00 AM – 6:00 PM</span>, providing families with the flexibility of a full day program.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Core academic instruction runs from <span class="font-bold text-green-600">9:00 AM – 4:00 PM</span>, when children engage in immersive learning and enrichment.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Flexible Schedule -->
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span> Flexible Schedule
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Families may select from <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">3 half days up to 5 full days</span> per week. We partner with you to design a schedule that works best for your family—providing a structured educational alternative to traditional daycare.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Calendar -->
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="text-2xl">📅</span> Calendar
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Open year round, only closed on <span class="font-bold text-green-600">national holidays</span> — convenient for working families.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <section class="py-12 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
             <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">FAQs for Anthem Families</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <!-- Local FAQ 1 -->
                    <details class="group bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4">
                        <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
                            Is Beibei Amigos near Anthem?
                            <span class="text-blue-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="ba-answer text-gray-600 mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-blue-200">
