                            <span class="text-blue-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="ba-answer text-gray-600 mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-blue-200">
                            More than ever. As the local public option sunsets, Beibei Amigos remains the <strong>exclusive provider</strong> of Mandarin and Spanish immersion accessible to Anthem families, ensuring your child captures this critical window for fluency.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <!-- General FAQ 1 -->
                    <details class="group bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4">
                        <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
                            Are you licensed?
                            <span class="text-blue-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="ba-answer text-gray-600 mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-blue-200">
                            Yes, we are fully licensed by the <strong>ADHS</strong>.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <!-- General FAQ 2 -->
                    <details class="group bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4">
                        <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
                            Sibling discount?
                            <span class="text-blue-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="ba-answer text-gray-600 mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-blue-200">
                            Yes! <strong>10% discount</strong> for siblings.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <!-- General FAQ 3 -->
                    <details class="group bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4">
                        <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
                            Potty training required?
                            <span class="text-blue-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="ba-answer text-gray-600 mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-blue-200">
                            Only for the 3-year-old classroom. We help train toddlers.
                        </div>
